      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"different path\" thing just sounds like more work. like i'm just choosing a different way to be lonely. it's not even about being authentic anymore, it's just... the constant noise of trying to exist in a world that wasn't built for me. i'm just so done with it. i feel like i'm running on empty and there's nothing left to fill it up with.",
