      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. but rest doesn't really work when you're always stuck in your own head. it's not just being tired, it's like... an fundamental wrongness. like i'm a glitch. i just wish i didn't have to feel this way anymore. i wish i could just find some actual peace.",
